:+1:.</p>]]></content><author><name>gaaaani(Seo Gaeun)</name></author><category term="markdown" /><category term="test" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[여기서 마크다운 형식으로 수정할 수 있습니다. 멋지게 사용해보세요 You can write regular markdown here and Jekyll will automatically convert it to a nice webpage. I strongly encourage you to take 5 minutes to learn how to write in markdown - it’ll teach you how to transform regular text into bold/italics/headings/tables/etc.]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">어서오세요</title><link href="https://gaaaani.github.io/blog/2025/07/27/my-first-post.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="어서오세요" /><published>2025-07-27T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2025-07-27T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://gaaaani.github.io/blog/2025/07/27/my-first-post</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://gaaaani.github.io/blog/2025/07/27/my-first-post.html"><![CDATA[<p>이건 내 <strong>블로그 첫 글</strong>입니다! 🎉</p>

<p>이제부터 개발 공부 기록을 차근차근 올릴 예정!</p>

